name: SERGIO
description:
Sergio has 4 hands in boxing. and it's lethal when it comes in tandem with his equally impressive right hook.

For virtually every minute of every round, sergio had his way with his younger foe, and he peppered him with hard, fast punches, sergio had hands so fast, that you could barely see his punches coming. They'd be thrown from all angles, in bunches and land with a tremendous amount of force that was amplified by the fact his opponent didn't see them coming.
